{"tid":435451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"江蘇悍婦與丈夫公路上吵架  用腳塞住軚盤 不讓開車","createTime":"2017-10-14T09:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T09:45:02.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"102efcd614c36a3b474c79945f73b1420dffcdcd","tid":435451,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:45:02.000Z","msg":"【與丈夫公路上吵架】<br />\n【悍婦用腳塞住軚盤 不讓開車】<br />\n<br />\n江蘇徐州有私家車停在高速公路不走，交警了解竟是夫妻吵架，妻子用腳按著軚盤不讓丈夫開車，並稱被丈夫毆打，又以髒話和不文手勢回贈交警。<br />\n<br />\n交警一番唇舌後終勸服妻子回乘客座，但仍要出動拖車把私家車移離現場。<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#高速公路<br />\n#夫妻吵架<br />\n#辛苦警察叔叔<br />\n#清官難審家庭事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1521892227955258/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1521892227955258%2F&d=xl8qb1EPxtlhBa4j0EbLgv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f8824fc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1521892227955258/</a>"}]}